{"_path":"/fitness/f004","_dir":"fitness","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"瑜珈 - 緩解焦慮的瑜珈動作","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":4,"category":"瑜珈運動","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-26T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"瑜珈-緩解焦慮的瑜珈動作"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"瑜珈 - 緩解焦慮的瑜珈動作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1.猫式和牛式伸展：这个体式可以激活脊柱，让呼吸和动作连接，让心慢慢安静下来。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"来到四脚板凳式，吸气延展脊柱，尾骨向上，腹部下沉，胸腔向前向上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"呼气低头弓背，背部肩胛骨找天花板，肚脐找后背。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"重复做 8-10 次。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-01.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-01.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2.谦卑战士式: 这个体式打开髋部和肩膀，当我们焦虑的时候这两个地方最紧了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从下犬式，右脚往前，后脚跟踩地，吸气双手往上来到战士一式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"然后双手来到身后，十指交扣。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"吸气打开胸腔，呼气往下折叠刀右膝盖内侧。保持 8-10 次深呼吸。然后换边重复。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-02.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-02.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3.坐立前屈折叠: 这个体式帮助你感恩、内省。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从坐立的体式，双脚并拢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"膝盖放松，深呼吸，呼气往前折叠。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果下背部比较紧，坐在毛毯或砖块上。保持 8-10 次呼吸。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-03.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-03.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4.支撑后弯: 后弯体式打开胸腔，扩张呼吸。在这个支撑的变体，胸腔部位打开更多，而且不需要做很深的后弯就可以"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坐下来，砖块放在身后。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"慢慢躺下来，砖块在肩胛骨的位置，双手在头后放松，保持 1 分钟。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-04.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-04.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5.扭转: 通过扭转释放负能量。每次呼气，扭转更多。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"躺下来，抱左膝盖靠近胸腔，双手“T”字形，左膝盖倒向右侧。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"看左侧。保持 8-10 次呼吸，换边重复。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-05.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-05.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6.倒箭式: 这个体式让神经系统平静下来，平衡循环系统，把你带到当下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"靠近墙躺下来，臀部靠墙，双腿靠墙并拢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"双手在身体两侧。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保持 8-10 次呼吸。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-06.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-06.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"7.靠墙 L 型头倒立: 头倒立增加血液循环，把氧气带到大脑，平静心情。这个变体更加安全。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量一下距离，双手离墙一条腿的距离。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"转过来，双手十指交扣，手肘压实地面，头顶点地。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"双腿慢慢踩墙向上，直到双脚和臀部同高。保持 8-10 次呼吸。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f004-07.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f004-07.gif"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"瑜珈-緩解焦慮的瑜珈動作","depth":2,"text":"瑜珈 - 緩解焦慮的瑜珈動作"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:fitness:f004.md","_source":"content","_file":"fitness/f004.md","_extension":"md"}